Equipment Archive
The ceiling is mirrored, perhaps to make it harder for anyone to sneak around without being noticed among the shelves.

/The equipment shelves here display an assortment of obsolete, broken, foreign, or otherwise unusual letter tools. (On the equipment shelves|There) are an accent flipper, an umlaut punch, a Catalan punt volat needle, some broken components, and some lamb granulates( on the equipment shelves)?. 

